	(text_box "Switches up to 4A (TPS2117) from +5V_USB or +5V_BUCK to +5V. Prefers buck over USB, threshold voltage is about 3.5V. The threshold voltage is low to prevent accidental switchover to USB during peak consumption (worst case in flight). Two diodes to ease the switchover."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
